data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLERS!

***LOAN ASSUMPTION OPPORTUNITY!!! Seller has an FHA loan locked in with a 2.8% Interest Rate that they are willing to reassign.***

Contemporary & inviting home in family-friendly subdivision!    This beautifully updated home has easy access to kids baseball, softball, and soccer fields and is right around the block from the local Country Club which has a swimming pool available for members!  Boasting a warm and inviting atmosphere, this residence offers a modern design, ample natural light, and a thoughtful layout that caters to the needs of today's families.

As you step through the front door, you'll be greeted by soaring walls and ceilings painted a bright white neutral color, large windows, which come together to create a bright and airy ambiance.  The open concept main floor seamlessly connects the living room + dining room + and kitchen making it ideal for entertaining and family gatherings - the laundry is on the SAME level as the bedrooms and kitchen!  

The sleek & stylish kitchen is a dream, featuring high-end stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and a small pantry.  Ample storage for your culinary needs - while the proximity of the eat in kitchen and formal dining room are adjacent for a seamless dining experience.

The main level features three spacious bedrooms - all are generously sized.  One of the highlights of this home is the lower level, with solid flooring and an open concept for either a fourth bedroom, recreation room, home office + entertainment area ... this flexible living space can be used for anything!  

Outside you'll find a professionally landscaped yard with a patio + deck + fire-pit area!  The possibilities are endless with this home.

This subdivision offers a sense of community with its parks, playgrounds, and walking trails, providing endless opportunities for outdoor recreation and quality time with loved ones.
